1.00	Robert_Weiss_MSW	Robert Weiss (therapist)	Robert Weiss, LCSW, CSAT-S is an international sexual addiction expert, author, educator and founder of the Sexual Recovery Institute, an outpatient sexual addiction and intimacy disorders treatment program in Los Angeles, Mr. Weiss is co-author of Cybersex Exposed: Simple Fantasy to Obsession , author of Cruise Control: Understanding Sex Addiction in Gay Men (ISBN 978-1555838218), and co-author of the just released, Untangling the Web: Sex, Porn and Fantasy Addiction in the Internet Age (ISBN 978-1555839680), along with numerous professional articles on sexual addiction.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/4/43/Robert_Weiss.png
